lls Risk management and project management skills Skill in prioritizing work & multi-tasking Excellent presentation, organization & client relationship skills Excellent Microsoft Office, ERP systems and data analytical skills Ability to travel as required to review current suppliersAbout this companySia Huat Pte LtdAgent, Direct Distributor and Stockist Sia Huat is Southeast Asia’s leading agent and direct distributor for an extensive range of foodservice products and equipment with over 40,000 SKUs of products and 120 brands. Our 40,000sqf ERP-enabled warehousing facility in Singapore ensures stocks are properly stored and monitored for ease of future replenishments. As the partner of choice, we strive to deliver beyond food service supplies to fit every budget and need. Sia Huat focuses on long-term relationships with our various partners in the food service industry. These include restaurants, hotels, airlines, hospitals, and educational institutions. We also work closely with our trade and wholesale customers, including resellers, and all major departmental stores. Today, Sia Huat exports to more than 13 countries in Southeast Asia and around the world.
